# Project Structure

This Flutter project follows a clean architecture pattern with clear separation of concerns:

```
lib/
├── main.dart                    # 应用入口
├── core/
│   ├── constants/              # 常量定义
│   ├── utils/                  # 工具类
│   └── theme/                  # 主题配置
├── data/
│   ├── models/                 # 数据模型
│   ├── repositories/           # 数据仓库
│   └── datasources/            # 数据源
├── domain/
│   ├── entities/               # 业务实体
│   └── usecases/               # 用例
└── presentation/
    ├── screens/                # 页面屏幕
    ├── widgets/                # 可复用组件
    └── providers/              # 状态管理
```

When creating new files, follow this structure and ensure they are placed in the appropriate directories.